condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description : No later than thirty (30) days after Effective Date, SASP shall update, ina manner satisfactory to the Association, the POM to reflect the new institutional arrangements under this Agreement.

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The MHSPP shall hire Financial Management and Procurement consultants, tobe responsible for fiduciary aspects of the Project implementation as part of the fiduciary team of the MHSPP, as set forth in thePOM. | Due Date :31-Aug-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The MHSPP shall sign a contract to procure, install and adapt automatedaccounting software system for the Project needs satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :30-Sep-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall amend the Procurement Plan to reflect the revisedimplementation plan and schedule. Such amendment will be subject to prior review and satisfaction by the Association. | Due Date:31-Jul-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II | Description :The Recipient shall monitor and evaluate the progress of the Project andprepare Project Reports in accordance with the provisions of Section 4.08 of the General Conditions and on the basis of indicatorsagreed with the Association. Each Project Report shall cover the period of six months, and shall be furnished to the Associationwithin 45 days after the end of the period covered by such report. | Frequency :SemiAnnual
